PN,39201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1771956278
OL,3,CDozens of staff on strike at school
OL,4,Ccomplain of pupils' 'violent' behaviour
OL,6,FDozens of staff have begun a nine-day
OL,7,Fstrike at a high school in Greater
OL,8,FManchester, citing 'violent and
OL,9,Fabusive' behaviour from pupils.
OL,11,FThe Teachers' Union members at St
OL,12,FCuthbert's RC High School in Rochdale
OL,13,Fhave begun their nine day strike
OL,14,Faction outside the school on Shaw Road
OL,15,Fat 8am on 24 February.
OL,17,FNASUWT have said that strike action
OL,18,Fwill take place between from 24-26
OL,19,FFebruary, 3-5 March and the 10-12
OL,20,FMarch.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1771956278
OL,3,CDozens of staff on strike at school
OL,4,Ccomplain of pupils' 'violent' behaviour
OL,6,FTeachers have said they are striking
OL,7,Fover the failure of leadership to
OL,8,Fprovide adequate staffing and
OL,9,Fresources and to put in place systems
OL,10,Fto address violent and abusive
OL,11,Fbehaviour from some pupils.
OL,13,FAmy Mills, Negotiating Secretary for
OL,14,FRochdale District for NASUWT: "We have
OL,15,Fbeen in negotiations here for the last
OL,16,F18 months around the health and safety
OL,17,Fof our members.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1771956278
OL,3,CDozens of staff on strike at school
OL,4,Ccomplain of pupils' 'violent' behaviour
OL,6,F"As a teacher, one of our biggest
OL,7,Fduties is to make sure that we are
OL,8,Fteaching future generations about
OL,9,Fwhat's right and what's wrong and what
OL,10,Fis going on in the school is really
OL,11,Fwrong.
OL,13,F"We've got staff and we've got
OL,14,Fteachers that are fearful to go into
OL,15,Ftheir workplace, they are being
OL,16,Fassaulted on a daily basis."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1771956278
OL,3,CDozens of staff on strike at school
OL,4,Ccomplain of pupils' 'violent' behaviour
OL,6,FSome staff members have been stamped
OL,7,Fon by pupils while on the floor, they
OL,8,Fhave been pushed and pregnant members
OL,9,Fhave also been pushed and shoved
OL,10,Fagainst walls.
OL,12,FShe added: "We have tried everything
OL,13,Fand exhausted all routes with the
OL,14,Femployer.
OL,16,F"When the trust took over, we have had
OL,17,Fan increase in violence since, we've
OL,18,Fhad a depletion in resources being put
OL,19,Finto the school and we have members
OL,20,Fthat have had life changing injuries
OL,21,Fas a result.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1771956278
OL,3,CDozens of staff on strike at school
OL,4,Ccomplain of pupils' 'violent' behaviour
OL,6,F"We've got Year 7 students that are in
OL,7,Ftears having panic attacks because
OL,8,Fthey are frightened about what they
OL,9,Fsee and that is wrong and as teachers
OL,10,Fwe have got a duty to make a stand
OL,11,Fagainst that and make a change.
OL,13,F"We've asked the employer to come to
OL,14,Fthe table several times and they've
OL,15,Fonly come to the table since the
OL,16,Fballot."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1771956278
OL,3,CDozens of staff on strike at school
OL,4,Ccomplain of pupils' 'violent' behaviour
OL,6,FThe union has been in dispute with the
OL,7,Ftrust for a year and a half and Ms
OL,8,FMills says that initially they were
OL,9,Fquick to get to the table where they
OL,10,Fhad "positive discussions".
OL,12,FWhen things were agreed, things began
OL,13,Fto improve for a "temporary period",
OL,14,Fbut since talks began, the school has
OL,15,Fhad four different head teachers,
OL,16,Fcausing what she has described as
OL,17,F"inefficient negotiations" where they
OL,18,Fare constantly asking if they can go
OL,19,Fback to what was agreed in previous
OL,20,Fdispute meetings.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1771956278
OL,3,CDozens of staff on strike at school
OL,4,Ccomplain of pupils' 'violent' behaviour
OL,6,FShe continued: "When we have asked
OL,7,Fthem to come back to the negotiation
OL,8,Ftable, they've said it needs to be at
OL,9,Fschool level, but what we have got is
OL,10,Fa changing person at the helm so
OL,11,Ftherefore we are getting
OL,12,Finconsistencies and the one thing that
OL,13,Fstudents and teachers need is
OL,14,Fconsistent, really clear boundaries
OL,15,Fabout what is okay and what is not
OL,16,Fokay.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1771956278
OL,3,CDozens of staff on strike at school
OL,4,Ccomplain of pupils' 'violent' behaviour
OL,6,F"As a teacher, the moral compass is
OL,7,Fmake sure that the future generations
OL,8,Fknow right from wrong and if we don't
OL,9,Fset those boundaries and maintain them
OL,10,Fand if we are being undermined then
OL,11,Fwhat does that tell our students?"
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
